data.description:
Welcome Home!  Lovely 4 Bedroom Home offers many amenities at this lower price point for this square footage! Open floor plan offers family room open to dining room overlooking large kitchen with bar height seating.  Great sized Master Suite with bathroom and large walk-in closet. Plus you get three more bedrooms including one Texas-sized that would be large enough for twins to share or why not, have an additional living area upstairs as well! Perfected by tile throughout entire downstairs and more!
Close proximity to Loop 375, restaurants and shopping!  Come by today to see your future Home Sweet Home!!
